5ï¸âƒ£ RBAC (Role-Based Access Control) ðŸ”‘
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
1.ServiceAccount Role ðŸ‘¤ ---> A Role defines a set of permissions for resources (like Pods, Services, etc.) within a namespace.

2.RoleBinding ðŸ” ---> Grants access based on a Role within a namespace.

3.ClusterRole  ---> Grants cluster-wide permissions like managing Nodes or Namespaces.

4.ClusterRoleBinding ðŸŒŽ ---> Grants access based on a ClusterRole across the cluster.
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
