+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
1.Node ðŸ— ---> Represents a worker machine in the cluster.

2.Namespace ðŸ· ---> A Namespace in Kubernetes is a logical partition within a cluster, 
                    that allows multiple teams or applications to operate in isolation.

